# 5. 鈍く、重く

Mafuyu's Mother: Oh... I didn't realize you were still doing that.
Mafuyu: (What did she mean by that?)
Mafuyu: (Does Mom think...?)
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: (Should I really keep attending?)
Mafuyu: (She said that it's okay for me to, but...)
Mafuyu: I'm back...
Mafuyu's Mother: Welcome home, Mafuyu. How was your club?
Mafuyu: We had an instructor from the archery federation come and teach us today.
Mafuyu's Mother: An instructor from the federation? That's incredible!
Mafuyu: How was your day, Mom?
Mafuyu's Mother: Hehe. I went to that exhibit I mentioned, and it was very good.
Mafuyu's Mother: Viewing masterpieces really does have a way of refining your taste.
Mafuyu's Mother: We should go together sometime. Of course, on a day when you don't have club activities.
Mafuyu: Oh...
Mafuyu's Mother: Ah, it's from your father. He says his meeting ended early, so he'll be home in time for dinner tonight.
Mafuyu: I see.
Mafuyu's Mother: Hehe. I'll need to get started right away.
Mafuyu: I'll help.
Mafuyu's Mother: Huh?
Mafuyu: Since I'm free, I'd like to help... Would that be alright?
Mafuyu's Mother: Yes...! Of course, dear!
Mafuyu's Mother: Let's surprise your father by preparing a delicious feast for him!
Mafuyu's Father: Oh, this mapo tofu's good. It has a nice kick to it.
Mafuyu's Mother: Hehe. I'm glad you like it. Mafuyu helped me make it today.
Mafuyu's Father: Really?
Mafuyu's Father: Thank you, Mafuyu. This is delicious.
Mafuyu: *Nod* I'm glad you like it.
Mafuyu's Mother: I'm so glad that we're able to spend time together like this again.
Mafuyu's Father: Yes, me too. It's certainly made everything feel brighter.
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu's Mother: I realized something now that we're living together again...
Mafuyu's Mother: I really didn't know anything about you, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu: Mom...
Mafuyu's Mother: I'm so impressed by the way you're doing your best with school, club and your hobby.
Mafuyu's Mother: You even did well on that test the other day. You must be putting in more effort than even I'm aware of.
Mafuyu's Mother: I feel that you have the power to succeed at anything you choose to do.
Mafuyu: I'm really not that special... But thank you.
Mafuyu's Mother: That reminds me. You mentioned that you wished to do something that allows you to be there for people, yes?
Mafuyu: I'm still not entirely sure...
Mafuyu: But I think I might...
Mafuyu's Mother: I see...
Mafuyu's Mother: Then, maybe we ought to start looking for schools for you.
Mafuyu's Mother: Based on your academic level, you should be able to get into any school you like, no?
Mafuyu: Thank you.
Mafuyu: But I want to keep thinking it over...
Mafuyu's Mother: Oh, I see...
Mafuyu's Father: Why don't we talk about this some other time, honey?
Mafuyu's Mother: Huh? Oh no...!
Mafuyu's Mother: I'm so sorry. I did it again...
Mafuyu: No, that's okay.
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu's Mother: It's also okay if you don't quite know what you want to do yet.
Mafuyu's Mother: You can take all the time you need to think about your future... While doing whatever you'd like to do now.
Mafuyu: (There's nothing wrong with this, right...?)
Mafuyu: (All Mom did was make a small suggestion, for my sake.)
Mafuyu: (But...)
Mafuyu: No, I'm having trouble focusing...
Mafuyu: I should get something to drink.
Mafuyu's Mother's Voice: Why...?
Mafuyu's Mother: Why did I say that?
Mafuyu's Mother: I thought I made it clear to myself that I'd respect Mafuyu's feelings...
Mafuyu's Father: ...
Mafuyu's Mother: Mafuyu said it was okay, but...
Mafuyu's Father: It's okay... Try not to beat yourself up.
Mafuyu's Mother: But...
Mafuyu: ...
